  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A cluster randomized trial to assess the efficacy of the Diabetes Medication Choice decision
      aid among Greek patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus compared with usual care. The tool
      will serve as a facilitator for the Shared Decision Making process.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
